headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Ulta Beauty (ULTA) After A 59% One Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether Ulta Beauty's share price still reflects good value or if most of the upside has already been priced in, it helps to step back and look at what the market is paying for the business today. Over the past week the stock recorded a 0.3% decline, while the 30 day return sits at 8.9%, the year to date return at 6.7%, and the 1 year return at 59.4%, compared with 30.2% over 3 years and 134.3% over 5 years.
